Hello there my fellow staff members and SCP’s I hope your having a great day. Anyway this here is my Artwork page for official Wiki of the Scp foundation. Special thanks to [[[http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/raddagher|raddagher]]] for teaching me how to create an art page.
I hope you all like my art here today, so anyways have wonderful day and take care.

------

++++ Why?

[[collapsible show="+ Title for showing text" hide="- Title for hiding text"]]
**I forgot the harness for Scp-5000**

[[/collapsible]]
